    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，三个Cluster。我确认一下：ClusterA里面是Ingress和Transform，ClusterB是Normalize和Enrich，ClusterC是Persist和Notify。每个Cluster内部这两个节点是顺序执行的对吧？",
