    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，内部都是单向箭头。然后阶段之间的连接是：Transform要连到Normalize，Enrich要连到Persist，最后Notify要回到Ingress形成闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
